<function>

access:   public

name: rangeLength

param: mixed, $value

param: mixed, $min

param: mixed, $max

param: bool, $blank, false

return: bool

</function>

Validate that the length of a value is within a given range.

* Parameters:

 * mixed //$value//: The value to validate.

 * mixed //$min//: The minimum valid length.

 * mixed //$max//: The maximum valid length.

 * bool //$blank//: Allow blank values to be valid.

* Returns bool: True if valid, false if not.